Question: Are there either any black couches or mirrors?

Reference Answer: no

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='couches')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)

ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'black' else 'no'")
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='mirrors')
ANSWER2=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER2} > 0 else 'no'")
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER1} == 'yes' or {ANSWER3} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
